('89370','30770','5','A gem of country house near Calvia'),
('89371','30771','5','In the outskirts of Calvia, in the southwest of Mallorca, stands this finca jewel on a 9.000m ² plot.  The Finca was renovated in 2006 with great attention to detail. From here it is only a short drive to the golf courses of Santa Ponsa, supermarkets, marinas and international schools.\r\nAbout a 150m long private driveway, past a park-like landscaped mediterranean garden, you reach the car port with 5 covered parking spaces. The well maintained property consists of 2 buildings.\r\nThe main house offers on the ground level the entrance hall, 3 bedrooms each with en suite bath room with shower, a bathroom with Jacuzzi and shower, living-dining room and a kitchen with a cosy breakfast room. All kitchen appliances are by Bosch including large fridge with ice maker for cool drinks.\r\nIn the first Floor is a master bedroom with dressing room, bathroom with tub and shower and 2 terraces. Storage rooms and a laundry room are available.\r\nA guest house with 40m ² has a bedroom and a small kitchen.\r\nSeveral covered terraces offers a beautiful view of the elaborate garden with carefully selected native flowers, shrubs and citrus trees.\r\nIn the cooler winter months, an oil fired central heating and in the warm summer an air condition provides a proper room temperature.\r\nA barbecue and the outdoor swimming pool, surrounded by sun terraces, complete the offer.\r\n'),
